                                <entry>in                                </entry>                                <entry>ev</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>Completion event, it is optional and can be NULL. The function will run in blocking mode if <emphasis>ev</emphasis> is NULL.</para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
